          "settings": {
            "title": "What is the fit like for the Bali Bikini & Banyak top?",
            "content": "<p>The Bali Bikini and Banyak bikini top is a smaller cut, designed to be firm so it doesn't move when being active.  If you prefer a more relaxed fee, size up and if in between go up two sizes.</p>"
