          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "title": "Does the Snow white colour go transparent when wet?",
            "content": "<p>All of our snow white seamless bikinis, crop top bikinis and crop rash guards are lined with beige econyl sustainable fabric to prevent them from going transparent when wet.</p>"
