        "accordion_pane_bnbVqP": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Do your one piece swimsuits have padding?",
            "content": "<p>Our one piece swimsuits are <strong>intentionally designed without padding</strong>. Thanks to the <strong>sculpted, panelled design</strong>, <strong>double lining</strong>, and a <strong>firm, supportive fit</strong>, there's no need for built-in cups. The one piece suit naturally holds you in, flatters your shape, and gives you all the support you need—without any shifting or bunching that often comes with padding.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_LiXp4q": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Which one piece suit provides the most UPF?",
            "content": "<p>If UPF protection is important to you, opt for the darker colours. The Sulawesi in Midnight provides the most UPF block out, due to the dark colour of the fabric and long sleeves.  Do keep in mind, the mesh on the side is not UPF.  If you want full block out, please use an SPF on the side of your body.</p>"
